{"date":"1935-01-05","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/63/38/132358_LIZyD.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/63/38/132358_LIZyD.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/63/38/132358_LIZyD.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/63/38/132358_LIZyD.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/63/38/132358_LIZyD.jpg"},"summary":"      热闹的森林里正在举行跑步比赛，参赛双方实力悬殊。一边是有蓝色飞毛腿之称的巨兔，另一边老态龙钟、步履蹒跚的老乌龟。巨兔傲慢无礼，丝毫不把这个无精打采的老家伙放在眼里，甚至对其肆无忌惮地嘲弄。老乌龟性格善良，对巨兔的恶意玩笑似乎全无知觉。随着一声枪响，巨兔如旋风一般冲出起跑线，而他的对手则被巨大的声响吓得缩入壳中。对手的软弱更令巨兔的傲慢肆意膨胀，他或者躺在路边睡觉，或者和赛道边上的小母兔们调情，或者炫耀其敏捷的身手。老乌龟则一如既往，坚定地向终点跑去…… \r\n　　本片荣获1935年奥斯卡金像奖最佳动画短片奖。","name":"The Tortoise and the Hare","name_cn":"乌龟与兔子","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":35,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":19,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1935","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"迪士尼","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Disney","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奥斯卡","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"龟兔赛跑","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欢乐","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"寓言","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1930s","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"音乐节拍剧","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"WilfredJackson","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1935年1月","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"排名低了","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"JeandelaFontaine","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"6(+1)","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1935年","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SillySymphonies","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1930-1939","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"undefined","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"短片&OVA","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"弱6","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"WaltDisneyPictures","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"子供向","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动物","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Short","count